text: The Jean Marie River First Nation, known as Tthets'ék'ehdélı̨ in its own Dene language, is a First Nations band government in the Northwest Territories. The band is headquartered in the community of Jean Marie River. The Jean Marie River First Nation is a member of the Dehcho First Nations. ==References== Category:First Nations in the Northwest Territories Category:Dene governments
title: Jean Marie River First Nation
